c: 7
v: 57
t: "Ni We wohereza imiyaga nk’ikimenyetso gitanga inkuru nziza, kibanziriza impuhwe ze (imvura), kugeza ubwo (iyo miyaga) ijyanye ibicu biremereye tukabyerekeza ahantu hakakaye, nuko tugatuma bitanga amazi (imvura) maze tukayeresha ibimera byose. Uko ni ko tuzazura abapfuye kugira ngo mwibuke"